originalSql:
SELECT 
    t.title AS movie_title,
    p.info AS person_info,
    a.name AS actor_name,
    ka.keyword AS movie_keyword,
    co.name AS company_name,
    ct.kind AS company_type
FROM 
    title t
JOIN 
    complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON cc.subject_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    person_info p ON a.person_id = p.person_id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword ka ON mk.keyword_id = ka.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name co ON mc.company_id = co.id
JOIN 
    company_type ct ON mc.company_type_id = ct.id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    t.title

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."PERSON_INFO", "t3"."ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."MOVIE_KEYWORD", "t3"."COMPANY_NAME", "t3"."COMPANY_TYPE", "t3"."production_year"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t1"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO", "t1"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "keyword"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "t1"."production_year"
FROM "company_type"
INNER JOIN ("company_name" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_name"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id") ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "t0"."id", "t0"."title", "t0"."imdb_index", "t0"."kind_id", "t0"."production_year", "t0"."imdb_id", "t0"."phonetic_code", "t0"."episode_of_id", "t0"."season_nr", "t0"."episode_nr", "t0"."series_years", "t0"."md5sum", "s1"."id" AS "id0", "s1"."movie_id", "s1"."subject_id", "s1"."status_id", "aka_name"."id" AS "id1", "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."imdb_index" AS "imdb_index0", "aka_name"."name_pcode_cf", "aka_name"."name_pcode_nf", "aka_name"."surname_pcode", "aka_name"."md5sum" AS "md5sum0", "person_info"."id" AS "id2", "person_info"."person_id" AS "person_id0", "person_info"."info_type_id", "person_info"."info", "person_info"."note", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id3", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"
RIGHT JOIN ("person_info" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t0" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t0"."id" = "s1"."movie_id") ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "s1"."subject_id") ON "person_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t1" LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "t1"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id") ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t1"."id"
ORDER BY "t1"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t1"."title") AS "t3"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "keyword", "phonetic_code"
FROM "keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."PERSON_INFO", "t3"."ACTOR_NAME", "t3"."MOVIE_KEYWORD", "t3"."COMPANY_NAME", "t3"."COMPANY_TYPE", "t3"."production_year"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."title" AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "t1"."info" AS "PERSON_INFO", "t1"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "s1"."keyword" AS "MOVIE_KEYWORD", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "company_type"."kind" AS "COMPANY_TYPE", "t1"."production_year"
FROM "company_type"
INNER JOIN ("company_name" INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_name"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id") ON "company_type"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_type_id"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT "t0"."id", "t0"."title", "t0"."imdb_index", "t0"."kind_id", "t0"."production_year", "t0"."imdb_id", "t0"."phonetic_code", "t0"."episode_of_id", "t0"."season_nr", "t0"."episode_nr", "t0"."series_years", "t0"."md5sum", "complete_cast"."id" AS "id0", "complete_cast"."movie_id", "complete_cast"."subject_id", "complete_cast"."status_id", "aka_name"."id" AS "id1", "aka_name"."person_id", "aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."imdb_index" AS "imdb_index0", "aka_name"."name_pcode_cf", "aka_name"."name_pcode_nf", "aka_name"."surname_pcode", "aka_name"."md5sum" AS "md5sum0", "person_info"."id" AS "id2", "person_info"."person_id" AS "person_id0", "person_info"."info_type_id", "person_info"."info", "person_info"."note", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id3", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"
RIGHT JOIN ("person_info" INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "title"
WHERE "production_year" >= 2000) AS "t0" INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "t0"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id") ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "complete_cast"."subject_id") ON "person_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t1" LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id") ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t1"."id"
ORDER BY "t1"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t1"."title") AS "t3"
